title: LET US HAVE THE POSITION WE CHOSE
body: IF I PICK JUNGLE I WANT JUNGLE NOT SUPPORT I WOULD RATHER WAIT LONGER TO GET WHAT I WANT PLEASE CHANGE THIS

replies.body: I agree, this is a serious problem, it really just ruins my day when I get autofilled
The alternative on OCE is queue times as long as or longer than a game. Not everyone has that kind of time.
